Package ohos.aafwk.ability.fraction

Class Fraction

  • java.lang.Object
    • ohos.app.AbilityContext
      • ohos.aafwk.ability.fraction.Fraction
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ILifecycle, Context

    public class Fraction
extends AbilityContext
implements ILifecycle
    Provides lifecycle callbacks of a fraction.

    A Fraction can be placed in a container (an Ability) as a part of its UI and cannot be used independently. The lifecycle state of a Fraction depends on its container. If the container is destroyed, all fractions in it will also be destroyed. You can use the Fraction to define a variety of layouts to enrich the user interface of your application.

    Since:
    4
